      "span_text": "Elevated baseline levels of CTACK/CCL27, MCP3/CCL7, MIF, and IP-10/ CXCL10, and a decrease in VEGFR1-positive monocytes from baseline to 24-h postaflibercept administration, have also been associated with improved response in glioblastoma patients [CITATION_1] .",
